DEFINITIVE VERDICT: PARTIAL CANCELLATION.

  - External quark Z_psi cancels exactly on the ratio.
  - Vertex corrections partially cancel at C_F prefactor but
    not at BZ-integrand level (Dirac/color-structure difference).
  - Gluon self-energy (C_A, T_F n_f) has no counterpart in Rep B.
  - Scalar-bilinear anomalous dim (-6 C_F) has no counterpart in Rep A.

The ratio's 1-loop correction retains the three-channel color
structure C_F * Delta_1 + C_A * Delta_2 + T_F n_f * Delta_3 with

  Delta_1 = 2 (I_v_scalar - I_v_gauge) - 6
  Delta_2 = I_v_gauge - (5/3) I_SE
  Delta_3 = (4/3) I_SE

All three channels are GENERICALLY NONZERO. Full cancellation
is REJECTED; no cancellation is also REJECTED (Z_psi cancels).

